  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n[[File:Icon Survival.png|link=Survival|frame|Tab Icon]]\n{{Quote|I love camping.|Woodie}}\n'''Survival Tab''' items and structures are generally useful things which can be [[Crafting|Crafted]] from the Survival Tab shown as a snare icon on the left side of the screen. Though some such as the [[Trap]] are always available, others must be unlocked with a [[Science Machine]], [[Alchemy Engine]] or a [[Blueprint]].\n\n==[[File:Gift Icon.png|32px]] Downloadable Content==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC, [[Siesta Lean-to]]s, [[Luxury Fan]]s, and [[Insulated Pack]]s were added to the Survival Tab.\n\nIn the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, [[Silly Monkey Ball]]s, [[Tropical Parasol]]s, [[Anti Venom]], [[Thatch Pack]]s, [[Palm Leaf Hut]]s, [[Tropical Fan]]s, [[Sea Sack]]s, [[Doydoy Nest]]s can be crafted and while playing as [[Warly]], [[Chef Pouch]]es in the Survival Tab. This DLC also includes the Siesta Lean-to.\n\nIn the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, [[Bug B'Gone]] repellent and the [[Bird Whistle]] can be crafted in the Survival Tab. Siesta Lean-tos and Insulated Pack are also available in this DLC.\n\n==Craftable Items and Structures==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted in the Survival Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><br /><gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nTrap.png|link=Trap|[[Trap]]\nBird Trap.png|link=Bird Trap|[[Bird Trap]]\nBug Net.png|link=Bug Net|[[Bug Net]]\nFishing Rod.png|link=Fishing Rod|[[Fishing Rod]]\nPretty Parasol.png|link=Pretty Parasol|[[Pretty Parasol]]\nUmbrella.png|link=Umbrella|[[Umbrella]]\nHoney Poultice.png|link=Honey Poultice|[[Honey Poultice]]\nHealing Salve.png|link=Healing Salve|[[Healing Salve]]\nCompass.png|link=Compass|[[Compass]]\nHeat Stone.png|link=Thermal Stone|[[Thermal Stone]]\nBackpack.png|link=Backpack|[[Backpack]]\nPiggyback.png|link=Piggyback|[[Piggyback]]\nStraw Roll.png|link=Straw Roll|[[Straw Roll]]\nFur Roll.png|link=Fur Roll|[[Fur Roll]]\nTent.png|link=Tent|[[Tent]]\nBundling Wrap.png|link=Bundling Wrap|[[Bundling Wrap]]\nSiesta Lean-to.png|link=Siesta Lean-to|[[Siesta Lean-to]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nLuxury Fan.png|link=Luxury Fan|[[Luxury Fan]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nInsulated Pack.png|link=Insulated Pack|[[Insulated Pack]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nAnti Venom.png|link=Anti Venom|[[Anti Venom]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nTropical Parasol.png|link=Tropical Parasol|[[Tropical Parasol]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSilly Monkey Ball.png|link=Silly Monkey Ball|[[Silly Monkey Ball]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nThatch Pack.png|link=Thatch Pack|[[Thatch Pack]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nPalm Leaf Hut.png|link=Palm Leaf Hut|[[Palm Leaf Hut]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nTropical Fan.png|link=Tropical Fan|[[Tropical Fan]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSea Sack.png|link=Sea Sack|[[Sea Sack]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nChef Pouch.png|link=Chef Pouch|[[Chef Pouch]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Warly Portrait|Warly}}\nDoydoy Nest.png|link=Doydoy Nest|[[Doydoy Nest]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nBug B'Gone.png|link=Bug B'Gone|[[Bug B'Gone]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nBird Whistle.png|link=Bird Whistle|[[Bird Whistle]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\n\n</gallery></div>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[fr:Survie]]\n[[ko:생존 탭]]"
